Research article

First published online March 29, 2024

The Curious Case of Vodafone Idea Merger: Is It a Saga of Turbulence or a Move Towards Potence?
===============================================================================================

[Chhavi Mehta](https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/10.1177/02560909241236548#con1), [Monika Chopra](https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/10.1177/02560909241236548#con2), and [Sanjay Dhamija](https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/10.1177/02560909241236548#con3)[View all authors and affiliations](https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/10.1177/02560909241236548#tab-contributors)

[Volume 49, Issue 1](https://journals.sagepub.com/toc/vika/49/1)

[https://doi.org/10.1177/02560909241236548](https://doi.org/10.1177/02560909241236548)

